#
# yauiclient-x11-legacy bundles the libraries below at install time under
# /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/. Each is built from upstream source by
# build-libmpv-linux.sh on Debian 11 and packaged into the libmpv runtime
# tarball.
#

Files: /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libmpv.so*
Copyright: 2000-2026 mpv developers and contributors
License: LGPL-2.1+
Comment:
 Bundled libmpv 0.41.0 from https://github.com/mpv-player/mpv
 Built with --disable-gpl flags throughout the toolchain so the resulting
 library is pure LGPL-2.1+ with no GPL-only components.

Files: /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libavcodec.so*
       /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libavformat.so*
       /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libavutil.so*
       /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libavfilter.so*
       /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libswresample.so*
       /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libswscale.so*
Copyright: 2000-2026 FFmpeg developers and contributors
License: LGPL-2.1+
Comment:
 Bundled FFmpeg 7.1.1 from https://ffmpeg.org/
 Configured with --disable-gpl, --disable-nonfree, so this build excludes
 every GPL-only component and ships as pure LGPL-2.1+.

Files: /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libplacebo.so*
Copyright: 2017-2026 Niklas Haas and libplacebo contributors
License: LGPL-2.1+
Comment:
 Bundled libplacebo 7.351.x from https://code.videolan.org/videolan/libplacebo
 Built with --disable-vulkan to avoid a Vulkan SDK runtime dependency.

Files: /usr/lib/yauiclient/lib/libluajit-5.1.so*
Copyright: 2005-2026 Mike Pall and LuaJIT contributors
License: MIT
Comment:
 Bundled LuaJIT from https://luajit.org/

